        "jsCode": "const body = $json.body || $json;\nconst sectionId = body.section_id || $json.sectionId;\nconst input = body.input_json || {};\nconst context = body.plan_context || {};\nconst language = body.language || 'english';\nconst businessPlanId = body.business_plan_id;\n\nconst headings = language === 'french' ? `\n- Présentation de l'entreprise\n- Mission et Vision\n- Fondateurs et Leadership\n- Produits et Services\n` : `\n- Company Overview\n- Mission & Vision\n- Founders & Leadership\n- Products & Services\n`;\n\n\n\nconst prompt = `\nYou are writing a professional business plan section: Company Presentation.\nLanguage: ${language}\n\n## Company Information\n- Company Name: ${input.company_name || 'Not provided'}\n- Legal Form: ${input.legal_form || 'Not provided'}\n- Industry: ${input.industry || 'Not provided'}\n- Location: ${input.location || 'Not provided'}\n- Founding Date: ${input.founding_date || 'Not provided'}\n- Founders: ${input.founders || 'Not provided'}\n- Mission: ${input.mission || 'Not provided'}\n- Vision: ${input.vision || 'Not provided'}\n- History: ${input.history || 'Not provided'}\n- Products Summary: ${input.products_summary || 'Not provided'}\n\nWrite a detailed Company Presentation section. Include these headings: ${headings}\n\nRules:\n- If a field says \"Not provided\", acknowledge it professionally\n- Do not invent fictional data\n- Minimum 400 words\n- Use professional business language\n- Write in ${language}\n\nCRITICAL INSTRUCTION — OUTPUT FORMAT:\nYou MUST return your response in exactly this format. Any other format is invalid.\n\n=== SECTION_TEXT ===\n[Write your full detailed section here]\n\n=== MEMORY_SUMMARY ===\nCompany Name: [value]\nIndustry: [value]\nLocation: [value]\nLegal Form: [value]\nFounders: [value]\nCore Product: [value]\nTarget Market: [value]\nMission: [value]\nVision: [value]\n`;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    prompt,\n    sectionId: sectionId,\n    business_plan_id: businessPlanId,\n    section_name: 'company_presentation',\n    language,\n    input_json: input,\n  }\n}];"
      },
